		About Us
	


Belleville Surgical Center28 North 64th St.Belleville, IL 62223Phone: 618-398-5705Fax:618-398-5764


 
View Map
 


Caring. Convenient. Cost-effective. State-of-the-Art. You will find Belleville Surgical Center is this and more.
Belleville Surgical Center was created for the convenience of the patient. We provide high quality and efficient service, with limited waiting time. Our experienced staff provides reassurance, personal attention, and top quality care to all patients and families! 
The design and goals of the facility compliment the physician’s schedule by starting and completing cases on time, having a quick turn over time between cases (ideally ten minutes), and our state of the art equipment. 
Quality, Safety, Commitment and Satisfaction are our goals! 






















